00:17.000 --> 00:19.600
Your aspirin, mademoiselle.

00:20.400 --> 00:23.000
I was starting to think
you'd forgotten about me.

00:23.000 --> 00:25.400
I was just looking for
a store that was still
open, that's all.

00:36.400 --> 00:37.700
Must be some headache.

00:38.800 --> 00:40.800
Can't even kiss your husband

00:40.800 --> 00:44.000
in the most beautiful city
on Earth.

00:44.600 --> 00:46.700
This isn't right, Kent.

00:47.300 --> 00:50.200
It's springtime in Paris.

00:51.000 --> 00:53.300
We're in the same room
we honeymooned in.

00:54.008 --> 00:56.500
Come on, maybe
a little Chardonnay

00:56.500 --> 00:57.800
will put you in
a better mood.

01:11.202 --> 01:12.709
To us.

01:19.609 --> 01:21.008
To us.

01:44.909 --> 01:46.003
You all right?

01:46.708 --> 01:47.902
What's going on?

01:48.306 --> 01:49.601
Were you dreaming again?

01:50.708 --> 01:53.801
An American couple in Paris...

01:53.806 --> 01:54.601
The wife ended up

01:54.605 --> 01:57.502
stabbing the husband through
the hand with a corkscrew.

02:01.006 --> 02:01.900
I don't know what to tell you.

02:01.906 --> 02:03.502
I don't think 'em up.

02:03.558 --> 02:07.872
www.forom.com presents

02:07.875 --> 02:11.882
Medium season 4 episode 3

02:16.447 --> 02:20.143
Transcript: www.ragbear.com

